      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-standard condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine cabin appointments, reflects a standard of care synonymous with a new acquisition. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision and responsiveness intended by its engineers. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to secure a specimen of unrivaled integrity.",
