    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly in showroom condition and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s incredibly clean inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
