    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97 Check out this absolute gem! I\u2019m parting ways with my car, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible, showroom-quality shape. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s basically like driving it off the lot for the first time. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is spotless. You\u2019ve gotta see it to believe how pristine it is! It's ready for its next adventure. Drop me a line if you're interested! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
