    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine E46 M3 in museum-grade condition. The S54 inline-six maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders, with the critical double-VANOS system recently overhauled and rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual to a variable M-differential. The chassis is flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution is fully realized. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection and zero deferred maintenance.",
